              S
              g
            
            g
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\frac {Tf}{f}}={\frac {Sg}{g}}}
  The right hand side depends only on 
  
    
      
        x
      
    
    {\displaystyle x}
   and the left hand side only on 
  
    
      
        t
      
    
    {\displaystyle t}
   so both must be equal to a constant 
  
    
      
